# Copy to ".env" in the repo root and set your value (".env" is gitignored).
# Used by scripts/trigger-add-submodules.sh and scripts/trigger-start-translation.sh
# (repository_dispatch API).
# Prefer GH_TOKEN; GITHUB_TOKEN is also accepted by the script.
#
# Token needs permission to create repository dispatch events on the target repo
# (classic PAT: repo / public_repo as appropriate; see GitHub REST API docs).

GH_TOKEN=
